Welcome.

11
00:1:21,600-->00:1:23,600
It's so nice of you to come.

12
00:1:23,600-->00:1:26,600
Oh, I just wanted to see your baby, Max.

13
00:1:26,600-->00:1:28,600
Hello, Rita Mae.

14
00:1:28,600-->00:1:30,600
I haven't seen you since the hospital.

15
00:1:30,600-->00:1:33,600
I'm Ellen Stewart, Marilyn's mother-in-law.

16
00:1:33,600-->00:1:34,600
