17
00:1:34,600-->00:1:35,600
How are you?

18
00:1:35,600-->00:1:36,600
How are you?

19
00:1:36,600-->00:1:39,600
Oh, and there is Max!

20
00:1:39,600-->00:1:43,600
Oh! My, how he's grown!

21
00:1:43,600-->00:1:47,600
A little present for Max.

22
00:1:47,600-->00:1:51,600
Oh, it's beautiful, Rita Mae!

23
00:1:51,600-->00:1:52,600
You shouldn't have.

24
00:1:52,600-->00:1:53,600
It's nothing.

25
00:1:53,600-->00:1:54,600
It's just a little present for Max.

26
00:1:54,600-->00:1:58,600
Can I get you some coffee or tea or a cold drink, Rita Mae?

27
00:1:58,600-->00:1:59,600
Oh, nothing, thank you.

28
00:1:59,600-->00:2:3,600
Well, I will leave you two to talk.

29
00:2:3,600-->00:2:5,600
Come on, you big guy.

30
00:2:5,600-->00:2:6,600
Yes, come on.

31
00:2:6,600-->00:2:8,600
That's it.

32
00:2:8,600-->00:2:9,600
It's nice seeing you.

33
00:2:9,600-->00:2:11,600
