34
00:2:11,600-->00:2:12,600
Thanks, Ellen.

35
00:2:12,600-->00:2:13,600
Thanks, Ellen.

36
00:2:13,600-->00:2:18,600
OK, Marilyn.

37
00:2:18,600-->00:2:20,600
You sounded like you've made a decision

38
00:2:20,600-->00:2:21,600
when you called me.

39
00:2:21,600-->00:2:24,600
I have made a decision, Rita Mae.

40
00:2:24,600-->00:2:26,600
I've decided to stay at home and be a full-time mother.

41
00:2:26,600-->00:2:30,600
I'm disappointed, but I respect your decision.

42
00:2:30,600-->00:2:33,600
If I had a child as cute as Max,

43
00:2:33,600-->00:2:34,600
I might do the same thing.

44
00:2:34,600-->00:2:36,600
But I haven't finished telling you

45
00:2:36,600-->00:2:37,600
