50
00:2:44,600-->00:2:47,600
Sounds interesting.

51
00:2:47,600-->00:2:49,600
Let me hear it.

52
00:2:49,600-->00:2:50,600
Do you remember

53
00:2:50,600-->00:2:52,600
our talks about custom-designed dresses for the boutique?

54
00:2:52,600-->00:2:53,600
I sure do.

55
00:2:53,600-->00:2:58,600
Why can't I design dresses for you here at home?

56
00:2:58,600-->00:3:0,000
And make them here.

57
00:3:0,000-->00:3:1,900
Have the fittings here, too.

58
00:3:1,900-->00:3:5,000
And I could do the selling and the pricing at the boutique.

59
00:3:5,000-->00:3:5,600
Exactly.

60
00:3:5,600-->00:3:7,600
Oh!

61
00:3:7,600-->00:3:9,600
What kind of dresses would you design?

62
00:3:9,600-->00:3:13,600
I've thought about that for some time.

63
00:3:13,600-->00:3:15,600
Yes?

64
00:3:15,600-->00:3:17,600
Wedding dresses.

65
00:3:17,600-->00:3:18,600
Wedding dresses?

66
00:3:18,600-->00:3:21,600
Brilliant idea!

67
00:3:21,600-->00:3:24,600
There's a big market today in wedding dresses.

68
00:3:24,600-->00:3:25,600
That's what I thought.

69
00:3:25,600-->00:3:26,600
I like the idea very much.

70
00:3:26,600-->00:3:28,600
And if it's successful,

71
00:3:28,600-->00:3:30,600
we can expand to all kinds of dresses.

72
00:3:30,600-->00:3:32,600
That's what I thought.

73
00:3:32,600-->00:3:34,600
As a matter of fact,

74
00:3:34,600-->00:3:37,600
I have a customer for your first wedding dress.

75
00:3:37,600-->00:3:39,600
My niece is getting married,

76
00:3:39,600-->00:3:42,600
and I've been trying to find just the right thing for her.

77
00:3:42,600-->00:3:45,600
Marilyn, you're going to design my niece's dress. Marilyn

78
00:3:45,600-->00:3:47,600
That'll be our first one,

79
00:3:47,600-->00:3:49,600
and then we'll use it to sell others.

80
00:3:49,600-->00:3:51,600
Do you really mean it?

81
00:3:51,600-->00:3:52,600
I really mean it.

82
00:3:52,600-->00:3:54,600
It's a simple idea, and it will work.

83
00:3:54,600-->00:3:57,600
You can certainly design dresses.

84
00:3:57,600-->00:3:58,600
I know that.

85
00:3:58,600-->00:4:1,600
And there's no reason why you can't do it from your home.

86
00:4:1,600-->00:4:3,600
I'm so excited!

87
00:4:3,600-->00:4:4,600
I can't wait to tell Richard!

88
00:4:4,600-->00:4:7,600
If I had a baby like Max,

89
00:4:7,600-->00:4:10,600
I'd want to stay home and be near him all the time, too.

90
00:4:10,600-->00:4:13,600
You're making the right decision

91
00:4:13,600-->00:4:15,600
for Max and for yourself too, Marilyn.

92
00:4:15,600-->00:4:17,600
It all sounds so easy.

93
00:4:17,600-->00:4:19,600
Now the hard work begins.

94
00:4:19,600-->00:4:20,600
Would you like

95
00:4:20,600-->00:4:23,600
